Package: starve
Title: Spatio-Temporal Analysis of Research Vessel data
Version: 0.17.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Ethan",
           family = "Lawler",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lawlerem@dal.ca")
Description: Fits hierarchical spatio-temporal generalized linear mixed models to
    point-referenced data in discrete time. Models are fit using maximum likelihood
    inference via the TMB (Template Model Builder) package. This package interfaces
    with the sf (simple features) spatial data package for ease of use. In
    addition to inference, models can be used to simulate data or predict at
    unobserved locations and/or at unobserved times.
License: GPL-3
